abstract: Vows column on wedding of Gabrielle Karol and Benjamin Jacobs.
lead_paragraph: They crossed the country on a joyous road trip and then abruptly separated. Five years later, they realize they belong together.

headline.main: Gabrielle Karol and Benjamin Jacobs: After Years of Breakup Regret, He Wins Back the One
